These smiling faces are some of your LIBOR Affiliate Members, who attended Friday's Affiliate Orientation Meeting at the Realtor® Building in West Babylon. During the orientation, LIBOR’s Affiliate Members had the opportunity to discuss all that is included in their Affiliate Membership and how best to utilize their membership to serve our Realtor® members. LIBOR’s Affiliate Membership Program provides Realtors® with value and opportunity to connect with local companies that offer a wealth of products and services. The Affiliate Membership Directory consists of over 190 businesses that offer a diverse range of goods and services with the Realtor® in mind. If you haven't done so already, take a look at the complete list of Affiliate members and what they provide – from Attorneys, Home Inspectors, lenders, closing gifts, vehicles, home improvement and so much more - LIRealtor.com/affiliates. If you love #FreeSaturday, you know that #freeculture is central to Common Root's mission. Free Saturday is a great example of how #CommonRoot brings free #resources directly to #community members.

A lot of our Free Saturday participants attend because they find valuable items and food for free, things they may not be able to afford otherwise. Others come to build #connections to like minded folks in the community, or to donate items they no longer need.

If you are someone who can afford a small donation to Common Root during #GivetoLincoln Day, I encourage you to do so. Your donations keep our events happening and our resources free for those who need them.

#QuestionEverything... because everything is a #lie. How, you ask? Pause, what is the textbook reason for these wars and military confrontations in these areas? #Terrorism, #isis, #rebels, the same song, over and over. Your childrens history books will name the cause as, "terrorism," but how they'll explain why the American military was unable to defeat #terrorists for 15 years, is beyond me. To enforce the idea of this threat within the hearts of the common citizen, are #falseflags, "terror events," perpetuated by the government, and media, who currently face a trillion dollar lawsuit for the complete fabrication of the unrelated #SandyHook incident. However in most cases, Taliban/AlQueda/Isis have accepted credit/blame, and real lives are lost, and they are literal sacrifices. Because their lives were taken to perpetuate a myth that resulted in loss of our rights, which is ultimately for their control, more importantly, it resulted in the loss of countless lives around the #world, loss of the #resources and #infrastructure from those countries, and again it's for their #control. If a country decides to not trade in #US #dollars or sell resources in dollars, it means the dollar is less circulated, and less circulation means less demand, and when demand is low but the supply is still high, what happens to the value? It drops. They (media/govt) could never say, that #911 #Iraq #Libya #Syria and #Russia are about money, but we know whenever the govt does something illogical, the reasoning can only be their obvious profit. So far 23 countries have "dropped the dollar" or bypassed the dollar in the global market, and Russia and China are next, so regardless if the media says the GOP or Dems are working with Russia, I'll guarantee they're the next villian. #WakeUp. 
Sidebar... did you ladies know that the reason you wear a bra, is a lie? #Nexttime.
